Package: OmicFlowR
Title: Automated Machine Learning Pipeline for Omics Data Classification
Version: 0.1.0.000
Authors@R: 
    person("Adrian", "Gutiérrez Domínguez", , "xagd99@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modular and automated framework for supervised classification of 
    omics data. Provides sequential functions for data preprocessing, feature 
    selection (using multiple methods including information gain, Relief, Boruta, 
    LASSO, and genetic algorithms), and model evaluation (k-Nearest Neighbors, 
    Naive Bayes, SVM, Neural Networks, Decision Trees, and Random Forest) with 
    cross-validation and parallel computing support..
